v 1.2026.06.02

The inital full release of ReterminateVT )formerly fakekmscom)
Pre-releases will be 0.yyyy.mm.dd, and releases will be 1.yyyy.mm.dd

ReterminateVT features recovery consoles that work in an initrd, and work similar to init=/bin/bash (init=/bin/recinit)

ReterminateVT features system consoles (vTTY) that run in userspace, that run as non-root, and can give way to display servers such as Weston

ReterminateVT features an option to use the fenrir screen reader for accessibility
